{"tid":2074764,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣外交部：釣魚台列嶼屬於台灣 不承認影響主權言行","createTime":"2020-06-22T10:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T12:23:34.000Z","uid":75656,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f58b45f7592dce1e589ea248e4655966bf56d22a","tid":2074764,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:50:34.000Z","msg":"對此，外交部透過新聞稿表示，釣魚台列嶼主權屬於台灣，任何意圖改變此事實的行為均屬無效，外交部已透過外交管道向日方表示遺憾及嚴正抗議。<br />\n<br />\n外交部重申，釣魚台是固有領土，台灣擁有主權的事實不容置疑，任何其他各方採取的片面主張及行為均無法改變這個事實。<br />\n<br />\n外交部強調，政府一貫堅持擁有釣魚台列嶼主權，今後仍將秉持和平理性方式，處理釣魚台列嶼主權問題。再次呼籲日方理性克制，勿以片面舉動干擾台灣對釣魚台列嶼的主權，避免影響東海穩定和平及台日友好關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202006220095.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202006220095.aspx&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F7XdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=65a0fc7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202006220095.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"b02ebfba77e53036e8bf6cfe4e5afe32fcf594d1","tid":2074764,"uid":37822,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:55:29.000Z","msg":"度度都話係自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如話係香港啦"},{"pid":"a8def2d6e710700843304c4b3a7582fa5e89a35d","tid":2074764,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b02ebfba77e53036e8bf6cfe4e5afe32fcf594d1","tid":2074764,"uid":37822,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:55:29.000Z","msg":"度度都話係自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如話係香港啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:56:54.000Z","msg":"講係咁講<br />\n台灣最無所謂<br />\n<br />\n心眼肚明<br />\n釣魚台係美國話係邊個就係邊個<br />\n<br />\n唔到佢地話事"},{"pid":"33f5cc54195210551e64c3c132b08a174a5ed626","tid":2074764,"uid":37822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a8def2d6e71070